textBeforeTable: Part Number Status for Givi Replacement Windshields - Suzuki Based on some other reviews, I thought this shield would dramatically reduce the wind resistance. In my experience the improvement was slight. I am 6 ft tall, so it might work better for shorter riders.Like some other reviewers, I also replaced the stock nylon screws with stainless steel screws and rubber washers. After I installed the shield, it was slightly cocked, so I loosened the screws and made several attempts to get a better fit, but could not.
